#~ "parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>colonna</replaceable></"
#~ "parameter>);\n"
#~ "String document.wordAt(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursore</"
#~ "replaceable></parameter>);"

#~ msgid "Returns the word at the given cursor position."
